WEBVTT

00:00:07.725 --> 00:00:11.711
♪I found a faint light
in the fading dusk♪

00:00:11.712 --> 00:00:15.311
♪And met your steady gaze♪

00:00:15.312 --> 00:00:24.132
♪One knowing glance,
and side by side we walk on♪

00:00:24.575 --> 00:00:27.061
♪Longing finds no place to rest♪

00:00:27.062 --> 00:00:29.211
♪Through drifting wind and rain♪

00:00:29.212 --> 00:00:32.699
♪You are the prayer within my hands♪

00:00:32.700 --> 00:00:40.324
♪A single second frozen,
tears in focus, my heart already knows♪

00:00:40.325 --> 00:00:42.786
♪We made a promise long ago♪

00:00:42.787 --> 00:00:44.786
♪For all our days to come♪

00:00:44.787 --> 00:00:48.449
♪You are the fate I cannot outrun♪

00:00:48.450 --> 00:00:53.836
♪How much must I let go
to trade for one moment?♪

00:00:53.837 --> 00:00:56.457
♪Holding you close♪

00:00:56.637 --> 00:00:58.874
♪Would that be enough?♪

00:00:58.875 --> 00:00:59.659
=Echoes of Love=

00:00:59.660 --> 00:01:01.499
(Adapted from the signed screenplay
Echoes of Love on Migu Reading)

00:01:01.500 --> 00:01:03.670
=Episode 17=

00:01:04.380 --> 00:01:05.411
How dare you.

00:01:05.412 --> 00:01:07.470
You set fire to the Drum of Grievance.

00:01:07.540 --> 00:01:10.058
Do you understand
the seriousness of this crime?

00:01:10.059 --> 00:01:11.299
Official, forgive me.

00:01:11.339 --> 00:01:13.698
I have a grave injustice to report.

00:01:13.699 --> 00:01:15.498
I accuse Grand Commandant Gao Deng

00:01:15.499 --> 00:01:17.899
and Zhou Zihua of Huanyue House.

00:01:17.900 --> 00:01:19.659
They formed the Shengtang Guild,

00:01:19.660 --> 00:01:21.258
using courtesans as enticement,

00:01:21.259 --> 00:01:22.659
to trade power and favor,

00:01:22.660 --> 00:01:24.019
and build their own faction.

00:01:24.300 --> 00:01:27.179
They colluded with fifty-six officials,
merchants, and men of influence,

00:01:27.699 --> 00:01:28.858
undermining the court

00:01:28.859 --> 00:01:30.299
and disregarding lives.

00:01:30.339 --> 00:01:31.739
There is a chart of their crimes

00:01:31.740 --> 00:01:33.099
and a register of names.

00:01:33.139 --> 00:01:34.179
I am a witness.

00:01:34.180 --> 00:01:35.698
The evidence is complete.

00:01:35.699 --> 00:01:37.299
I ask the official to investigate.

00:01:37.940 --> 00:01:39.060
Bring it forward.

00:01:57.540 --> 00:02:00.280
The evidence will remain in my custody
for presentation in court.

00:02:00.280 --> 00:02:02.360
But you burned the Drum of Grievance.
The offense is serious.

00:02:02.360 --> 00:02:03.539
Detain her pending trial.

00:02:04.537 --> 00:02:07.459
(And you think you can
bring down the Shengtang Guild?)

00:02:09.900 --> 00:02:11.498
Song Zhiyun stands accused,

00:02:11.499 --> 00:02:13.280
having filed charges
against Grand Commandant Gao Deng

00:02:13.280 --> 00:02:15.620
and Zhou Zihua of Huanyue House.

00:02:15.860 --> 00:02:18.099
As witness and evidence are in place,

00:02:18.180 --> 00:02:21.220
Huanyue House and
the Shengtang Guild are to be sealed.

00:02:21.580 --> 00:02:23.538
Further evidence will be gathered,

00:02:23.539 --> 00:02:24.780
and judgment rendered thereafter.

00:02:25.150 --> 00:02:28.532
(The Court of Judicial Review)

00:02:29.260 --> 00:02:30.979
Song Zhiyun,

00:02:31.539 --> 00:02:33.859
it seems Official Gu
has cast you aside as well.

00:02:34.379 --> 00:02:36.259
Retribution never fails.

00:02:39.379 --> 00:02:41.778
Who would have thought
we would end up like this,

00:02:41.779 --> 00:02:43.780
locked in the same cell?

00:02:44.099 --> 00:02:46.060
You caused the deaths of so many.

00:02:46.980 --> 00:02:49.180
Do not compare yourself to me.

00:02:50.460 --> 00:02:51.938
You simply do not understand.

00:02:51.939 --> 00:02:54.060
Everything I did was for your sake.

00:02:54.379 --> 00:02:56.739
Since you chose this life
in the pleasure quarters,

00:02:56.740 --> 00:02:58.979
you should have known the cost.

00:02:59.539 --> 00:03:02.060
If I had not
managed things so carefully,

00:03:02.740 --> 00:03:05.378
how would you have met Gu Chengye,

00:03:05.379 --> 00:03:06.859
or Shanguan Yu?

00:03:08.460 --> 00:03:10.699
She was my finest creation.

00:03:11.099 --> 00:03:12.778
I gave her my full devotion,

00:03:12.779 --> 00:03:14.460
yet she disregarded it all.

00:03:14.939 --> 00:03:15.938
For your sake,

00:03:15.939 --> 00:03:17.900
she defied me at every turn.

00:03:18.460 --> 00:03:20.780
Now that she has fallen to this end,

00:03:21.300 --> 00:03:23.979
she does not even come to see me.

00:03:24.499 --> 00:03:26.099
Shanguan Yu.

00:03:27.339 --> 00:03:29.300
You still dare speak her name?

00:03:29.980 --> 00:03:31.419
It was because of you,

00:03:31.779 --> 00:03:33.340
because of your Shengtang Guild,

00:03:34.250 --> 00:03:35.690
that she died.

00:03:41.819 --> 00:03:43.300
She is dead?

00:03:46.939 --> 00:03:49.099
I warned her long ago

00:03:49.300 --> 00:03:51.780
to stay away from you.

00:03:52.499 --> 00:03:53.900
But she would not listen.

00:03:55.580 --> 00:03:56.620
And now,

00:03:57.059 --> 00:03:59.259
she has lost her life as well.

00:04:15.740 --> 00:04:20.220
The flute player is gone,
the jade tower stands empty.

00:04:20.580 --> 00:04:23.619
With whom shall I lean in shared sorrow?

00:04:38.339 --> 00:04:39.298
She was simply...

00:04:39.299 --> 00:04:41.580
She was too stubborn.

00:04:42.060 --> 00:04:44.220
She could not even protect herself,

00:04:44.539 --> 00:04:46.659
yet she insisted on shielding others.

00:04:47.380 --> 00:04:49.460
You have no idea how it pained me.

00:04:50.700 --> 00:04:52.699
I should have sent her away long ago,

00:04:52.700 --> 00:04:55.020
far from this place of turmoil.

00:04:55.512 --> 00:04:57.236
But I could not leave,

00:04:57.237 --> 00:04:59.059
nor could I send them away.

00:05:00.339 --> 00:05:02.340
It was too late.

00:05:03.212 --> 00:05:05.059
Too late.

00:05:09.979 --> 00:05:11.460
Do you think

00:05:12.380 --> 00:05:14.780
I committed every wrong
in Huanyue House?

00:05:15.900 --> 00:05:18.460
Huanyue House was not always like this.

00:05:18.500 --> 00:05:20.338
In those days, Madam

00:05:20.339 --> 00:05:23.259
taught us to sing and dance, the qin,
chess, calligraphy, and painting.

00:05:23.260 --> 00:05:25.939
I was once her most favored pupil.

00:05:25.940 --> 00:05:27.499
Those were

00:05:27.700 --> 00:05:29.499
the happiest days of my life.

00:05:30.179 --> 00:05:32.499
You mean Haitang Madam?

00:05:33.060 --> 00:05:34.619
What a pity.

00:05:34.620 --> 00:05:39.161
When Haitang became Ruyi,

00:05:39.162 --> 00:05:41.282
everything changed.

00:05:42.380 --> 00:05:43.379
So,

00:05:43.380 --> 00:05:44.218
Haitang Madam

00:05:44.219 --> 00:05:46.499
was indeed killed by Madam Ruyi?

00:05:46.539 --> 00:05:48.220
And what of it?

00:05:52.099 --> 00:05:54.379
What could you possibly do to them?

00:05:54.380 --> 00:05:55.940
Only I

00:05:56.620 --> 00:05:58.459
labored in silence,

00:05:58.460 --> 00:06:00.299
waiting for the right moment,

00:06:00.460 --> 00:06:03.570
only to become
their scapegoat in the end.

00:06:04.739 --> 00:06:07.900
Official Gu, Commander
of the Imperial Guard, has arrived.

00:06:11.179 --> 00:06:13.580
There are hidden circumstances
in the Shengtang Guild case.

00:06:13.659 --> 00:06:16.059
It is now under
the Imperial Guard's authority.

00:06:16.060 --> 00:06:18.419
The officials implicated
have been released.

00:06:18.425 --> 00:06:19.436
At present,

00:06:19.437 --> 00:06:22.197
we are here to interrogate
the principal suspect, Song Zhiyun.

00:06:22.512 --> 00:06:23.439
Yes.

00:06:23.940 --> 00:06:25.859
The Shengtang Guild

00:06:26.700 --> 00:06:28.298
truly can

00:06:28.299 --> 00:06:33.419
turn the tides at will.

00:06:42.979 --> 00:06:44.099
Gu Chengye.

00:06:46.575 --> 00:06:48.416
I exhausted every scheme,

00:06:49.419 --> 00:06:51.499
and weighed countless outcomes.

00:06:52.700 --> 00:06:55.499
But I never imagined
Shanguan Yu would die.

00:06:55.859 --> 00:06:56.780
I...

00:07:00.339 --> 00:07:02.179
In the end, I still lost.

00:07:16.299 --> 00:07:17.419
No.

00:07:18.099 --> 00:07:19.580
We will win.

00:07:25.080 --> 00:07:29.382
(Gu Residence)

00:07:51.140 --> 00:07:53.099
You have not eaten for days.

00:08:04.339 --> 00:08:05.739
I found this

00:08:06.179 --> 00:08:07.220
in her hand.

00:08:10.380 --> 00:08:11.780
She kept it with her all along.

00:08:32.100 --> 00:08:34.224
♪Night rain falls before the courtyard♪

00:08:34.225 --> 00:08:38.974
♪Illuminating the partings
of the mortal world♪

00:08:38.975 --> 00:08:45.375
♪Strangers meet again,
the past ablaze in vivid hues♪

00:08:46.255 --> 00:08:47.979
♪A sharp arrow pierces through memory♪

00:08:47.980 --> 00:08:49.494
Take me to her.

00:08:49.495 --> 00:08:53.199
♪Longing spreads like ink♪

00:08:53.200 --> 00:08:55.658
♪Beaded curtains divide love
and hate at either end♪

00:08:55.659 --> 00:08:57.180
Take me to her.

00:09:00.421 --> 00:09:03.778
♪After endless sorrow endured
love is a word too hard to sever♪

00:09:03.779 --> 00:09:05.180
Do not look for her.

00:09:05.419 --> 00:09:07.259
I have already laid her to rest.

00:09:07.425 --> 00:09:11.261
♪Past ties fade
like a dream gone cold♪

00:09:11.262 --> 00:09:13.934
♪In giving all, we found our only joy♪

00:09:13.935 --> 00:09:17.574
♪That year we laughed
beneath pear blossoms♪

00:09:17.575 --> 00:09:20.578
♪One night of snow
fell wild and restless♪

00:09:20.579 --> 00:09:22.580
Let her remain in your memory

00:09:23.380 --> 00:09:25.300
as she was at her most radiant.

00:09:28.075 --> 00:09:31.574
♪With blood upon my heart,
I bid love farewell♪

00:09:31.575 --> 00:09:35.570
♪No more longing will enter my dreams♪